ardour (1:5.11.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  [ Jonas Smedegaard ]
  * Update copyright info:
    Drop copyright field from header section.
  * Update copyright info:
    Use https protocol in initial format line.
  * Update copyright info:
    Fix double-space-delimit authors.
  * Update copyright info:
    Consistently use fully expanded name of author QMUL.
  * Tidy copyright info:
    List debian dir as last Files section.
  * Update copyright info:
    Fix limit coverage for copyright holder Apple.
    Use SPDX license shortname AML.
  * Modernize Vcs-* fields:
    Use git (not cgit) in path.
  * Modernize cdbs:
    Do copyright-check in maintainer script (not during build).
  * Fix drop README.source section about special care for CDBS:
    Directly contradicts section emphasizing
    that *no* special care is needed (CDBS users handle merges).

  [ Jaromír Mikeš ]
  * New upstream version 5.11.0
  * Bump Standards.
  * Patches refreshed.
  * Bump Standards.
